      • refreshVisuals

        public void refreshVisuals()
        The refreshVisuals of this EditPart(all shape editparts) updates the text(shorten shape name), the boundaries and the tooltip(complete shape name) of the Shape figure. The refreshVisuals of this EditPart the names of all roleTypes and roleGroups in the child Model are added to the rolePart and the method ORMSuperShapeEditPart.refreshVisuals() is called.
        Overrides:
        refreshVisuals in class ORMSuperShapeEditPart

      • addChildVisual

        protected void addChildVisual(EditPart childEditPart,
                  int index)
        In case of this EditPart that would be the figure of a Segment. When the user uses the data view on the editor the second segment(operation segment) isn't added to the contentPane. In case of this ORMCompartmentEditPart that would be the figure of a Model. If the figure of the Model or the rolePart is added to this compartment depends on which version of the compartment figure is used also if the user has steped into thr compartment or not. ( the adding of segment figures is handelt through calling ORMShapeWithSegmentEditPart#addChildVisual(EditPart, index).
        Overrides:
        addChildVisual in class ORMShapeWithSegmentEditPart
